==English==

===Noun===
'''barn'''  (''plural:'' '''[[barns]]''')
# A [[building]], often found on a [[farm]], used for storage or keeping animals such as [[cattle]].
# (''nuclear physics'') A [[unit]] of [[surface area]] equal to 10<sup>-28</sup> [[square metre]]s.

